// vitest setupFile — skip the entire e2e suite when BUNNY_E2E !== '1'.
// Tests `it.skipIf(skip)(...)` against the exported flag; no globalThis hacks.
// Also asserts BUNNY_ACCOUNT_KEY is present when the gate is open, since
