**Success Criteria:**
- ✅ `bunny deploy --dry-run` shows plan without side effects
- ✅ `bunny deploy` idempotent on unchanged files
- ✅ Warm run <3s (measured locally)
- ✅ Credentials from configure used by deploy
- ✅ 429 retried with backoff, succeeds
